ome new innovations he had planned for The Washington Post, which, as Bezos=
 acknowledged, =E2=80=9Cpunches above its weight=E2=80=9D when it comes to =
negative headlines. =E2=80=9CWe saved The Washington Post once, and we will=
 save it again,=E2=80=9D he said, noting that the paper had experienced six=
