viate that kind of retaliatory action by an incoming administration.<br/><b=
r/><i>Figliuzzi</i>: I think two things can be true at the same time. We co=
uld view this as a horribly unfortunate set of events and
wish it hadn=E2=80=99t happened, and at the same time, we can say we unders=
