me whenever the justice system is further eroded. It=E2=80=99s eroded enoug=
h=E2=80=94largely because of Donald Trump, not Joe Biden=E2=80=94but this d=
oesn=E2=80=99t help with public credibility. At the same time, I=E2=80=99m =
also the father of adult sons. The concept that Pam Bondi is going to overs=
ee the Bureau of Prisons under a Trump administration, where my son could b=
e subjected to everything under the sun if he=E2=80=99s incarcerated, might=
 be enough for me to say, <i>I=E2=80=99m not letting that happen</i>.<br/><=
/td>
